    <Paragraph Type="Character">
      <Text>WALT</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Ah. Kjeldahl-style recovery flask, 2000 milliliters. Very nice. You got your Griffin beakers, you got your volumetric. But check this out --the piece de resistance. Round bottom boiling flask, 5000 milliliters.</Text>
