    <Paragraph Type="Scene Heading">
      <Text>EXT. BUNGALOW DUPREE SITS ON HIS FRONT PORCH, DRINKING A LONG-NECK BEER AND GLOWERING. WALT'S NISSAN PUTTERS INTO VIEW, REVERSES AND BACKS INTO DUPREE'S DRIVEWAY. WALT CLIMBS OUT, JAZZED. AFTERNOON</Text>
