    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Scene Heading">
      <Text>EXT. BUNGALOW -GARAGE/BACK YARD CHEMICALS, LABWARE, SUPPLIES --THE LAST OF THE CARLOAD OF STUFF WALT BROUGHT GETS PACKED INTO A BACK CORNER OF DUPREE'S MESSY OLD GARAGE. DUPREE COVERS IT WITH A TARP. AFTERNOON</Text>
