    <Paragraph Type="Scene Heading">
      <Text>INT. CREDIT UNION THE NAME ON THE WALL SAYS "ONTARIO TEACHERS CREDIT UNION." IT'S CLOSING TIME. WE FIND WALT STANDING AT THE COUNTER, DOING BUSINESS WITH A TELLER AND A BRANCH MANAGER. CLOSER --CRISP ONE HUNDRED DOLLAR BILLS GET COUNTED OUT. AFTERNOON</Text>
