    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Nah. Come on, man! Some straight like you, giant stick up his ass ••• all a sudden at age, what, fifty he's just gonna break bad?</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Scene Heading">
      <Text>EXT. PARKING LOT CLOSE ON A FAT HANDFUL OF CASH. DUPREE COUNTS IT, IMPRESSED. WE'RE IN A SHOPPING CENTER LOT, MOSTLY EMPTY. IN B.G. IS THE CREDIT UNION. DUPREE AND WALT SIT IN DUPREE'S DAYTONA. AFTERNOON</Text>
