      <Text>INT. DRESSING ROOM IT'S TIGHT IN HERE. FAMILIAR CRUTCHES LEAN AGAINST THE WALL. WALTER, JR. SITS ON A BENCH, STRUGGLING TO PULL A STIFF NEW PAIR OF OFF-BRAND JEANS OVER HIS BARE LEGS. NIGHT</Text>
