      <Text>Skyler is dismayed he's not standing up for their son. Frustrated. until she notices:</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action">
      <Text>NEW ANGLE --the jock is still flogging the joke as WALT enters frame behind him. Unbeknownst to everyone, Walt has quickly looped around, stalking up behind these guys.</Text>
