    <Paragraph Type="Character">
      <Text>DUPREE</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Acceptable? Every jibbhead from here to Timbuktu's gonna want a taste! It's gonna be like, "Sir, would you care to replace your Schwinn bicycle with this brand-new Ferrari?" Shit!</Text>
