    <Paragraph Type="Action">
      <Text>Brand-new giant screen TV. Otherwise, this place looks like a cross between a frat house and a crack house. KRAZY-8, a young, hard-looking Mexican, sits on a sofa dotted with cigarette burns. He's playing NBA basketball on his PS2.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
