    <Paragraph Type="Scene Heading">
      <Text>INT. KRAZY-8'S HOUSE MORNING</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character">
      <Text>DUPREE</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Huh? See? Crystal so big, look like somebody broke a window. Look like you'd cut your nose off. Try it.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action">
      <Text>Krazy takes a whiff of the open baggie, considers. He scoops a taste into his pinkie nail and snorts it up his nostril.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character">
