    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character">
      <Text>DUPREE</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Hell, yeah I'm back! with a vengeance I Nigga gotta make a living! And with your cousin gone away and all •••</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Parenthetical">
      <Text>(changes gears)</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>And listen homes, about that. It really broke me up about Emilio. Dude is like my brother.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Parenthetical">
      <Text>(mournful)</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>He okay? You talk to him?</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character">
      <Text>Krazy-8</Text>
    </Paragraph>
